{"tid":228043,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"應該點做 老豆好嬲屋企隻貓","createTime":"2017-05-03T15:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T05:20:35.000Z","uid":84568,"like":3,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff55dab275e080f92a8695fee8ef5a9d185f0230","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"唔係第一次嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係咁 我隻貓成日周圍柯尿<br />\n但近排已經好啲 少左咁做<br />\n所以老豆呢排同佢相處得幾好<br />\n我心諗 幾好呀佢地fd咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知 今日老豆抱貓貓<br />\n貓貓好大力咬佢塊面<br />\n搞到我老豆塊面流血<br />\n好嬲咁講 佢食埋呢包餅就唔養佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都唔係第一次講<br />\n我真係分唔清佢講真定講假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我應該做啲乜 <br />\n教貓貓 我有教過 但佢唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n氹左老豆先 可以呀 但下次問題再出現 又點搞？<br />\n唉好無助呀 俾啲建議呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想無咗隻貓貓<br />\n<br />\n題外話 老豆成日話我拎左佢翻黎<br />\n貓盤又唔洗 糧又唔餵 乜都唔做<br />\n我而家改咗喇！我想問除左呢啲仲有無乜嘢可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07f2edea3ddbba0114a2d81e39518bf2ddc009c","tid":228043,"uid":97634,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"唔要你老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2095a7443ef06a87d2b1468a574253d4ae81c9e3","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0731489bbd6b67e41e4a64a290651f5e0318c5","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔要你老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f09a3cc6c63078adcbaf2fa022592f8f4c4dacf","tid":228043,"uid":45450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"叫你老豆咪掂佢住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教好隻貓先"},{"pid":"40707795c5d592988027ca42512cdaac79e5b63a","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e408fe44f2f45d6dae9fd0b42a7ced9628b4bd0","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你老豆咪掂佢住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教好隻貓先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點教 有冇方法 試過同佢傾計 無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e8f7fdb1b9e0e2cb7aa482b1bad585e69141c0","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"揾人入黎教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bed1069b7228f43eb135733198bef0dbdfa47fe","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f472780e1459c34cd583bfa8741824ba207b97","tid":228043,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"扎咗隻貓"},{"pid":"2072d0a37a6d5589af8edde46ea2e1a19f8cfd52","tid":228043,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8619f95caf75e8c8c06f0a535a776ad799557cc8","tid":228043,"uid":5566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"reply