 我試過教佢<br />\n同佢講 但佢唔聽<br />\n所以我上黎問下有冇咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家要教佢 可以諗帶佢結紥 買竉 仲有冇 <br />\n我都想負翻應有嘅責任</blockquote><br />\n你同隻貓傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你隻貓識人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到咁程度，係一做錯，一係好兇咁喝<br />\n一係捉住佢頸壓住佢<br />\n同佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心你知屋企點，就買布偶嗰啲貓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼親人任你舞都唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbaadb7df635f5bf965bc2449d502298bd7829f5","tid":228043,"uid":84568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真回<br />\n<br />\n首先帶去絕育先<br />\n然後除咗教貓都要教你老豆<br />\n貓唔係公仔，佢唔一定想你抱，你夾硬抱佢梗係攻擊你<br />\n你試下喺街見到個女仔幾得意走去抱下，鼻都咬甩你<br />\n<br />\n最後，keep住refill 包糧咪唔會有食完嘅一日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多謝你 我知點做 我會學做一個有責任心嘅主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd58a20e5914344377411a2c5bdaa7342997bea0","tid":228043,"uid":34246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"你每晚偷偷加返d 餅落個袋度"},{"pid":"b40aeee6c841dc05f59c6aaeed4e267d