ets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eca1344bc56db3a2f2f15d4597e3e2845ec491","tid":228043,"uid":41687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"你隻貓未結扎 <br />\n所以會周圍柯尿搶地盤宣洩主權<br />\n加上未扎會好易暴躁 <br />\n貓唔係隻隻都中意同人親近<br />\n嗰個moment 唔想人掂就唔比你掂<br />\n通常佢身體或者聲音一定有警告你老豆<br />\n你老豆強行抱或者抱得唔啱都會大打出手<br />\n代表佢忍無可忍<br />\n<br />\n我唔係9up <br />\n你可以睇Jackson galaxy 或者 my cats from hell 你就知好多時唔係隻貓痴撚線而係個主人無知<br />\n<br />\n貓有得教嫁 你睇完努力教下你老豆同貓貓啦"},{"pid":"df27711d30bdff162d5a051fcbbd013e7ee94b91","tid":228043,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"貓冇得教<br />\n佢唔鍾意就唔鍾意<br />\n我估你貓唔鍾意比人抱，但老豆偏要抱佢<br />\n要同你老豆講隻貓唔鍾意咁，叫佢唔好咁做<br />\n你老豆如果都唔聽就準備同貓搬出去住la<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 過來人"},{"pid":"5052b4b31b0a29e00f5d79a80e82bb8e3c607bda","tid":228043,"uid":41687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下jackson galaxy學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMy cat from hell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早我一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab01ee7f7f90770cbdf9386eefde05a681959673","tid":228043,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:32:11.000Z","msg":"同隻貓講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6712d6ed98a57600609cbb44a1e4e181959e06","tid":228043,"uid":41687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓冇得教<br />\n佢唔鍾意就唔鍾意<br />\n我估你貓唔鍾意比人抱，但老豆偏要抱佢<br />\n要同你老豆講隻貓唔鍾意咁，叫佢唔好咁做<br />\n你老豆如果都唔聽就準備同貓搬出去住la<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓係有個性 唔代表無得教"},{"pid":"b0ee73fa66f1fe34f472af9dc5fbeaf06a0d1b7f","tid":228043,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬最尾幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連呢d基本野都唔做，你會肯拎時間出嚟教佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4bd00af3359daa5806fc7610679f497e06c2d3","tid":228043,"uid":22902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"你隻貓幾大有冇絕育?貓發情係會周圍屙<br />\n如果隻貓有潔癖而個廁所又未凊，都有機會咁做<br />\n<br />\n至於咬人個度，係咪你老竇唔識同佢玩，而隻貓又唔鍾意咁玩，佢咬得塊面就一定係距離好近，一係你買多d玩具呀木天蓼呀畀你老竇同佢玩，減少用身體同佢接觸令佢知道身體唔係玩得嘅野<br />\n<br />\n不過樓主點都要小心d，佢一下趁你出咗去就放走貓就麻煩"},{"pid":"96eac091ce6374ae8f194f22ca42e668dbe90bf2","tid":228043,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"拎少少錢買D貓草睇下隻貓會唔會冇咁暴躁<br />\n測試用途可以先買平既<br />\n如果唔貴買幾款試下先"},{"pid":"f7a2885bcff4d9000bdedcf204f66ffe83b91d67","tid":228043,"uid":41687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解釋翻<br />\n係我講得唔清楚 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實傾計係指 佢坐係度 我指住佢<br />\n問佢 做乜又周圍柯尿？<br />\n語氣唔係傾計咁<br />\n我真係講到19999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓會feel到你情緒<br />\n鬧無用 <br />\n要同狗一樣用獎勵制 同用聲音棒(有click click聲嗰種)<br />\n平常唔可以比零食<br />\n係每做啱就click一下同有零食<br />\n等佢知咩係啱咩係錯<br />\n<br />\n睇my cat from hell la"},{"pid":"d7ee0912833537b98c641ec0c3198d1941102901","tid":228043,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">貓盤又唔洗 糧又唔餵 乜都唔做</span><br />\n一開始帶返黎要人地屌先做 貪得意？<br />\n所有寵物唔撚係玩具 要養就應該一早自動自覺去做<br />\n利申 冇養貓 養狗養龜養魚"},{"pid":"00d3517ff83381bd9ae726168798f91bcd2bcbe6","tid":228043,"uid":80966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a552cfbb391cc6b2bc9bc02246b96f71c3a5cc33","tid":228043,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貓冇得教<br />\n佢唔鍾意就唔鍾意<br />\n我估你貓唔鍾意比人抱，但老豆偏要抱佢<br />\n要同你老豆講隻貓唔鍾意咁，叫佢唔好咁做<br />\n你老豆如果都唔聽就準備同貓搬出去住la<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓係有個性 唔代表無得教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多人係expect 可以好似教狗咁教佢地<br />\n唔聽話就打到佢地聽為止<br />\n但貓唔受呢套<br />\n<br />\n睇tv 有d 寵物訓練師會用貓既行為模式去教<br />\n如你所講貓性格問題，唔係每一次都成功"},{"pid":"8ce70725c14944984efa36e109e3f8a76126ac3d","tid":228043,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"掉左隻貓佢啦 主人都抓 冇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1c0c9689c471746f033d72dbad2800d63b46d4","tid":228043,"uid":11381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾人類區區為左隻貓。。。貓奴真係貓奴 自稱奴隸都制</blockquote><br />\n隻貓仲重要過老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8b8b394b88fd559c04ef9d4d8805ae14577e25","tid":228043,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你條仆街<br />\n唔養你就真<br />\n咩叫有教但唔聽呀<br />\n姐係你教錯囉</blockquote><br />\n樓主咪撚生仔啊 肯定係垃圾父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fbb098f062a4a8b1db7bf5639918ed9f126c40","tid":228043,"uid":73533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:47:04.000Z","msg":"留名幫樓主 養老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac363b68cd79f23c1755f807a34e5b54a935182","tid":228043,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T16:47:50.000Z","ms